# Node template downloaded with gut

**/*.db
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
**/node_modules
**/dist
# NOTE: lib/ and linux_amd64/ are intentionally NOT excluded here.
# They contain LanceDB native libraries (.so/.a) required for CGO compilation.
# Fly/Depot COPY lib/linux_amd64/ /usr/local/lib/lancedb/ in Dockerfile.local.fly
!lib/
!include/

